welcome: Hello! Welcome to the Builderment Seeds! Here you can search for any seed you want! This website is made by {{Space.yg}} and {{Human-Crow}}.
tip1: Click on a seed to copy.
tip2: Click on a number at the Resource column to get an accurate amount.
note1: The World Size and Resource Amount are available only to people with advanced world settings. If you do not have advanced world settings, the default for both is 100%.
